{"tid":283542,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"又點估到我會係髮型屋幫自己洗頭","createTime":"2017-06-14T08:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-14T11:03:57.000Z","uid":12680,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1fc25361a9d05c49d2f80bb450c97fc5c3f65c5","tid":283542,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"今日fd生日 同佢出去食飯<br />\n又見d頭毛好撚長<br />\n於是就去剪個頭啦<br />\n點知平時去開果間今日冇開<br />\n唯有近地地附近搵間 <br />\n入到去中撚哂伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身見冇乜人<br />\n有個髮型師坐係到玩電話<br />\n以為好快到我剪<br />\n個髮型師叫我坐低 幫我著哂袍<br />\n點知等左十五分鐘 都未幫我洗頭<br />\n我趕時間就催下條友<br />\n佢先肯幫我洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗到一半 聽到佢d同事返黎幫佢買埋外賣<br />\n佢就出撚左去食野<br />\n我訓係到等左佢十分鐘到仲唔撚返黎<br />\n佢d同事又唔幫我洗埋佢<br />\n我再催佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ：唔該師父 趕時間 可唔可以快小小<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ： 食埋隻脾黎<br />\n<br />\n嬲撚到我 掉轉個身自己幫自己洗<br />\n洗撚完出去頭都唔吹 放低廿蚊洗頭水錢就走左<br />\n<br />\n而家個頭濕住咁搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fd80b0695f52ed97ab112ba67fd8043201d1d88","tid":283542,"uid":11381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:53:52.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"3dfcc0ca47c45a1542e6f549ffd8e619d75a7838","tid":283542,"uid":12680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece98c80b6faeed87f373a870b0f58e298c5d632","tid":283542,"uid":7049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T09:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過一入到去即刻幫我洗頭 但等左成個鐘先剪 最後自己吹頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要鬼死咁大冷氣"},{"pid":"53feb11d05db24f666e224e358f59b57c1108d57","tid":2